<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2">
<p><milestone unit="altchapter" n="1"/>  Primum itaque domino deo, rectori custodique nostro, <lb/>
            ineffabiles ago gratias, quod me de sanctis fratribus et coepiscopis <lb/>
