<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="6">
<p>Denique in eo libro, ubi illa capitula Pelagius scripsit, <lb n="10"/>
            huic positioni, qua dixit <choice><sic>lomnes</sic><corr>omnes</corr></choice> uoluntate propria regi et suo <lb/>
