<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="22">
<p><milestone unit="altchapter" n="20"/> Non enim fides dubitat christiana, quam noui <lb/>
            haeretici obpugnare coeperunt, et eos, qui lauacro regenerationis <lb n="5"/>
